# Changelog

## 2026-06-26

### Sidebar → Central Hero Panel
- Moved `<aside class="sidebar">` out of the grid layout, above the main content
- Transformed into a centered floating card (`.sidebar.hero`):
  - Centered horizontally with `max-width: 600px; margin: 60px auto`
  - Card background (`var(--surface)`), rounded corners (24px), box shadow
  - Profile picture made circular (`border-radius: 50%`), 150×150px with border and shadow
  - Links reorganized from vertical column to horizontal centered row
  - Download CV button changed to `display: inline-block` with `padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 14px`

### Layout Change
- `.layout` changed from 2-column CSS grid (`320px 1fr`) to single-column centered layout (`max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto`)
- Mobile media query adjusted accordingly

### Collapsible Text with Arrow Toggle
- Added `TEXT_COLLAPSE_LINES` constant in `js/data.js` (default: 3 lines)
- Collapsible content implemented for:
  - **About & Contact** section — arrow icon on the right of the `h2` header
  - **Education** cards — arrow icon on the right of each card title
  - **Experience** cards — arrow icon on the right of each card title
- Uses `images/down_arrow.png` as the toggle icon
- Arrow rotates 180° when expanded via CSS `transform: rotate(180deg)`
- CSS classes added: `.section-header`, `.card-header`, `.toggle-arrow`, `.collapsible-content.collapsed`

### Markdown-driven News & Projects Cards
- Created `news/` and `Projects/` folders for `.md` files
- Each `.md` file uses YAML frontmatter: `title`, `date`, `image` (optional)
- Added `NEWS_FILES` and `PROJECTS_FILES` arrays in `js/data.js` listing the `.md` files
- `js/main.js`:
  - `parseFrontmatter()` — extracts YAML frontmatter from `.md` files
  - `mdToHTML()` — converts basic markdown (bold, italic, links, images, lists, headers) to HTML
  - `loadMarkdownList()` — fetches each `.md` file, parses it, and renders cards in a grid
- Layout: image in top half, title/date/description in bottom half
- If no `image` is specified in frontmatter, a lightblue placeholder (`#dbeafe`) is shown instead
- `news-grid` and `project-grid` share the same responsive card layout
- Added CSS: `.news-grid`, `.news-card`, `.card-content`, `.card-date`, `.card-description`, `.card-img-placeholder`

### Link icons & hero card centering
- Replaced text links (Email, GitHub, LinkedIn, Scholar) in hero card with 24×24px icon images (`images/mail.png`, `github.png`, `linkedin.png`, `scholar.png`)
- Added hover opacity effect on icon links
- Added `width: 100%` to hero card to ensure proper centering

### Institution logos in Education & Experience cards
- Added `logo` field to EDUCATION entries pointing to `images/logos/`
- Fixed EXPERIENCE logo paths from `images/organizations/` to `images/logos/`
- Cards now show a 40×40px logo on the left of each card header
- Added CSS: `.institution-logo`

### Smaller news/project cards with text truncation
- Reduced card image height from 220px to 120px
- Reduced card content padding to 14px, smaller font sizes
- Description text truncated at 3 lines with ellipsis (`-webkit-line-clamp: 3`)
- Smaller border radius (8px instead of 12px)

### Publication filter buttons — text-only
- Removed borders and button background from year filter buttons
- Now displayed as underlined accent-colored text links

### Awards — single card with 3-column grid
- Replaced individual cards with a single `.card` containing a 3-column grid (`.awards-grid`)
- Each award shows name + year in a compact list layout
- Added CSS: `.awards-grid`, `.award-item`
